big data<br />\n識揀一定揀computer linguistic<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nling+stat路過表示comp ling唔用big data發展點發展<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係話少data嘅就唔應該做"},{"pid":"aba4848070632a22680987ffd6ad8cd6c6258fb7","tid":458151,"uid":70989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T05:43:12.000Z","msg":"係既，但點解一定要留香港撈？"},{"pid":"102ce34e72ce75bcaf92938665a38d3465de48ee","tid":458151,"uid":69779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T05:43:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>垃圾big data<br />\n識揀一定揀computer linguistic<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nling+stat路過表示comp ling唔用big data發展點發展<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係話少data嘅就唔應該做，如果唔係 endangered language無人會理<br />\n<br />\n但係 major language嚟講big data一定係將來必走路向之－<br />\n<br />\n前幾年 lsa summer school先搞過 big data theme</blockquote>"},{"pid":"478907204549d10502a1e833a286bf28975da30d","tid":458151,"uid":148531,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T05:45:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>垃圾big data<br />\n識揀一定揀computer linguistic<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nling+stat路過表示comp ling唔用big data發展點發展<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n寫language + translator啦 我想用neural net去recognize啲complex grammar<br />\n<br />\n目前啲language analysis都係未detect到commoner language features例如slang, inversion同難度高嘅rhetoric<br />\n<br />\n如果用neural net可以搵到呢啲grammar嘅origin<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 今日嘅google translate嘅quality會高好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雖然我係自學computer language construction<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbig data = big brother = stopla<br />\n<br />\n最憎big data收集個人資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"399d2c173077211f95398db3ced0f640d3580c8f","tid":458151,"uid":69779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T05:45:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係既，但點解一定要留香港撈？</blockquote><br />\n放棄巴係連登ml神人，我哋要好好向佢學習<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0297d42515eeb21e0c902b1da99e17681e4d6677","tid":458151,"uid":70989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T05:46:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係既，但點解一定要留香港撈？</blockquote><br />\n放棄巴係連登ml神人，我哋要好好向佢學習<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又吹奏我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2749f618b88305ce7d4d2f47e24551b165db525a","tid":458151,"uid":148531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T05:47:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係既，但點解一定要留香港撈？</blockquote><br />\n放棄巴係連登ml神人，我哋要好好向佢學習<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又吹奏我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0a5384153cc4a296f0e3eb6259f14b85098a065","tid":458151,"uid":69779,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T06:00:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>垃圾big data<br />\n識揀一定揀computer linguistic<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nling+stat路過表示comp ling唔用big data發展點發展<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n寫language + translator啦 我想用neural net去recognize啲complex grammar<br />\n<br />\n目前啲language analysis都係未detect到commoner language features例如slang, inversion同難度高嘅rhetoric<br />\n<br />\n如果用neural net可以搵到呢啲grammar嘅origin<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 今日嘅google translate嘅quality會高好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雖然我係自學computer language construction<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbig data = big brother = stopla<br />\n<br />\n最憎big data收集個人資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打係cs個邊？我係pure ling嘅，所以係用返pure角度睇<br />\n<br />\n咩叫啲grammar嘅origin<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  未grammaticalise之前嘅意思？<br />\n<br />\n同埋slang呢啲似係lexicon多個grammar<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nwrt big data，咁你做呢啲個training set又點嚟？switchboard個類大corpus都好難detect到啲rare啲嘅linguistic phenomenon，如果要掘得深入啲（尤其係已經好多人研究過嘅major language），真係要擴大個database<br />\n<br />\n同埋如果唔收集個人資料嘅話，analysis上始終會有問題，因為有時其實age，gender呢啲係confounding factor，如果唔control返會有simpsons paradox嗰類inference問題<br />\n<br />\n況且socioling好多時呢啲factor就係variables of interest<br />\n<br />\n所以我覺得collect個人資料都係難免<br />\n<br />\n只要你collect之有道，唔好scrape埋唔雖要嘅資料，我覺得ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}